Package: ConFluxPro
Type: Package
Title: A Toolkit for Soil Gas Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Valentin","Gartiser",email = "valentin.gartiser@student.uni-tuebingen.de",role = c("aut", "cre"),comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5320-374X"))
Description: A collection of different functions that help analysing soil gas profiles. It implements different approaches for flux calculation based on the gradient-flux method and includes an inverse model for production-based flux estimation.
